{"tid":2453622,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"財經新聞：天命基金「連燈力」呂布軍盤中以$33.53矇頭入陣SOXL ! 再次聽天命 !","createTime":"2021-03-19T14:41:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T17:09:12.000Z","uid":149018,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"328ede3fa65ad878a49611ec2c268ce089374cac","tid":2453622,"uid":149018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:41:44.000Z","msg":"第十八次軍議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2453509/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2453509/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/arJ64pJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FarJ64pJ.jpg&h=ada9f234&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9LLM4pN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9LLM4pN.jpg&h=f210b8ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ww4Q4N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ww4Q4N.jpg&h=94f353f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RSYu2bw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRSYu2bw.jpg&h=b13a1dd5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第十七次，呂布聽天命盤前以$35.89山頂之勢進攻TKAT，未己以立刻獲利，其後突然下趺止蝕無效無人接貨卻是天機所示。呂布軍憑天下無雙之勢令TKAT重返$39.7後果斷斬殺！錄下史無前例之+10.62%大勝！<br />\n<br />\n第十八次軍議，呂布再次聽天命放棄思考，直接專注進軍SOXL，看人勝、天勝，還是天助人勝？<br />\n<br />\np.s.赤兔隊目前正以$26.75以一周圍城戰術智取PLTR至周一，形勢不妥。<br />\n<br />\n呂布軍「連燈力」目前戰況17戰6勝11敗，勝率現為35.29%！<br />\n目前「連燈力」呂布狀態：<br />\n武力100 智力80，「連燈力」大將 呂布剩餘<span class=\"green\">888.94</span>HP 累計虧損<span class=\"red\">7.21</span>%<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"green\"><span class=\"xx-large\">呂布曰：乜尻新聞財報利好消息都係廢，矇眼抽股更為上策</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3UYVBE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3UYVBE.jpg&h=e468de5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/13zia9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F13zia9Z.jpg&h=4461a71a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RpFYa9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRpFYa9Z.jpg&h=8dd3c014&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"592d9a773f6a5f4a7f6bef658f3ad90c0b2248b0","tid":2453622,"uid":246023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe790e7a66734f3b9ad58420e88c0d2703f3976","tid":2453622,"uid":373910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:43:05.000Z","msg":"將軍連呢隻都想燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b50a0a577c37a0cb04f946d0b3c75c5ab650cb","tid":2453622,"uid":303090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"好嘢將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c12bc0ce44dafc4d31868772dd124bb4abb92bc9","tid":2453622,"uid":346744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:43:40.000Z","msg":"報告將軍<br />\n小女子願意獻身"},{"pid":"e26248742cca303de48fc54a66ed1b595efa1efb","tid":2453622,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:44:00.000Z","msg":"我f呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e742b0d38b3402958c59def8689d19c57f56405","tid":2453622,"uid":2638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a8e76eb4b76fcfe6dd92391e6f1ed8b4d556f77","tid":2453622,"uid":149018,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T14:45:09.000Z","msg":"連登，我在想...<br />\n當我不必分心想選股，專注在運氣之上時，<br />\n世上還有人敢誇口...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4YYZE4F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\